"pid":"eecf74479b586fdee0859d0d9c2ed92fb924fcf3","tid":739141,"uid":98915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c1b0ee56595e3ed0371b1c24d33c22e56908eea","tid":739141,"uid":47924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T15:09:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T15:11:04.000Z","msg":"咁你同學係幾好"},{"pid":"9bca23c198bdbd6769c4ca295d309e8b7e5f3679","tid":739141,"uid":71755,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T16:09:00.000Z","msg":"好有同感，我讀IT類嘅engine，寫開program，想同同科嘅朋友討論下D技術野都好難。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如我近排玩緊某種programming framework，想分享下我學到/發現到嘅野，<br />\n又或者我發現左有D咩好嘅free online course想推薦下比佢地，但佢地都係hea9我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問佢地對咩技術有興趣，佢地會答你寫下app囉，但講幾句就已經露曬底，乜都唔知唔識，口講有興趣但從來都唔會自己睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我有諗過會唔會係我有興趣果D fields同佢地唔同呢，但我從來冇見過佢地會自己會睇咩課外野，自己研究咩新技術，一講呢tech野就hea9我，平時D話題都係講食/玩/睇戲/女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇人話講呢D話題唔好，但作為讀呢科嘅人係咪應該要對自己果科有返少少興趣呢？<br />\n<br />\n如果佢地本身比逼讀呢科，GPA低，冇心讀嘅都算。奇就奇在佢地班人都係成績中上，甚至GPA好高嘅人來，正常成績好嘅人或多或少都會對自己major有返咁上下興趣，但係佢地身上我睇唔到呢樣野，甚至令我覺得佢地冇興趣做乜讀呢科，佢地又唔係冇得揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bee785124ef6b5a38bf65ce0bf946c69bcda441","tid":739141,"uid":98915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bca23c198bdbd6769c4