smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aea7eb5ed73d71a090032fe35d419449c8724ada","tid":739141,"uid":7458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T16:39:24.000Z","msg":"我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n身邊既朋友冇興趣 論都冇的討<br />\n我想討論既野佢地全部都唔明<br />\n我鐘意有關歷史 太空既野<br />\n一講親佢地就會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人明呢種感受?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d78dfbd7b255672beab5d3d513c77e4faea215","tid":739141,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T17:28:23.000Z","msg":"習慣左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91f9ce4ad139d007c3789387a64d7a86f0aa593a","tid":739141,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T17:35:54.000Z","msg":"宜家好少人會坐係度一齊討論學術<br />\n一係冇興趣一係覺得煩"},{"pid":"9424cf9cfefa67e203247efda1ad52dec3563177","tid":739141,"uid":98915,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"91f9ce4ad139d007c3789387a64d7a86f0aa593a","tid":739141,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T17:35:54.000Z","msg":"宜家好少人會坐係度一齊討論學術<br />\n一係冇興趣一係覺得煩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T17:48:21.000Z","msg":"有時就係太多呢種情況<br />\n搞到我都驚咗同人講學術嘢<br />\n好似俾人太認真咁<br />\n但我份人係停唔到思考<br />\n我覺得完全冇都唔諗唔識<br />\n日日只係尋開心 反而會好depress<br />\n完全冇深度交流真係好咩"},{"pid":"83424d51466fc42c240fcc6fe55c8b2e5409db41","tid":739141,"uid":64003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T18:17:37.000Z","msg":"初學藝術者留名"},{"pid":"03f0ec9b719c21a715d1586a993d05a66e755a6b","tid":739141,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T18:19:11.000Z","msg":"連登都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d488589e959006294126e7b0a49c129afcd56c56","tid":739141,"uid":126973,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T18:19:59.000Z","msg":"玩到深入